Origins: According to the Bakersfield Police Department, Shy'ann Michelle Renee Wells is missing, but because she is classified as a runaway her name is not currently listed on the web sites of organizations that track missing children.
Example: [Collected on the Internet, July 2012] Someone is circulating on Facebook a poster of a missing girl, "Shy'ann Michelle Renee Wells." It says "Bakersfiend" andhas a Los Angeles area code of 661-327-7111. Of course there's no mention of where she was last seen, under what circumstances, or WHEN she was lastseen.
Claim: A 14-year-old girl named Shy'ann Michelle Renee Wells is missing from her California home.
